profile:
QUALITY ELECTRICAL SERVICES IN THE REGIONAL MUNICIPALITY OF WOOD BUFFALO

Immanuel Electric’s team of trained and qualified technicians is equipped to handle all jobs, big and small, from fixing single residential electrical outlets to commercial wiring upgrades for the electronics and equipment of a 21st century business. We work on both new construction and on renovations for both your home and business.

Immanuel Electric Ltd. opened its doors in July of 2003 in order to offer superb electrical services to the regional municipality of Wood Buffalo. Kyle Forrest, Master Electrician, and Minard Presley, Journeyman Electrician, founded this growing enterprise after providing electrical services throughout British Columbia for over 12 years. During our time in Fort McMurray, we have grown from a 2-man operation to include up to 14 employees at any given time.



Immanuel Electric Ltd. has grown by over 300% since 2003, going from a small operation specializing in commercial maintenance to an electrical business sought out by residential and commercial building contractors, business owners and homeowners alike. We have 4 fully-equipped service vehicles to serve our clients’ needs and our electrical staff has over 30 years of experience. We offer quality service by qualified electricians at fair-market prices for residential, commercial and maintenance projects.



With a bright future in sight, Immanuel Electric Ltd. is striving to maintain the personal touch of a small business while providing state-of-the-art technical skills to our clients. "Reliability, Honesty and Excellence – The Way We Do Business."
